24:28.868 --> 24:29.600
That hurt, Charlie.

24:29.602 --> 24:33.471
Why you want to hurt the man
that taught you everything?

24:33.473 --> 24:36.640
Everything that we
talked about inside?

24:38.511 --> 24:39.610
I kept you safe,

24:39.612 --> 24:42.313
