39:55.494 --> 39:57.594
You're not gonna believe this.

40:00.132 --> 40:03.266
About an hour ago,
I was supposed
to be down here.

40:03.268 --> 40:06.069
Charmain called, so I wasn't.

40:06.338 --> 40:07.837
Roy wanted me here.

40:07.839 --> 40:11.274
He didn't
actually do it, though.
None of the Satans did.

40:11.276 --> 40:15.078
Charmain was
with them all night
at the Bleu Room.

40:19.418 --> 40:21.751
Need a homicide detective.

40:22.187 --> 40:23.787
You think?

40:38.370 --> 40:43.206
Disarmed.
Not a gunfight. An execution.

40:43.442 --> 40:45.341
You see any casings?

40:45.343 --> 40:46.643
No.

40:46.645 --> 40:49.279
'Cause this was
done with an M16.

40:49.581 --> 40:52.048
Carried one for two tours.
I know the holes.

40:52.050 --> 40:53.550
So M16s eject casings.

40:53.552 --> 40:56.619
Six head shots.
Should be six casings.

40:56.621 --> 40:59.522
Shooter's very buttoned-up.

41:00.058 --> 41:03.993
The shooter is U.S. Military.

41:06.531 --> 41:08.531
RALPH: Charlie boy.

41:10.101 --> 41:12.802
Bring your ass on
out here, Charlie.

41:14.372 --> 41:15.905
Charlie boy!

41:28.153 --> 41:29.519
(EXHALES)

41:32.557 --> 41:37.193
It's been coming
for a long, long time now.

41:38.663 --> 41:41.531
This country's gonna burn.

41:45.504 --> 41:48.371
You see it, don't you?

41:48.773 --> 41:52.709
The war that's been brewing
for over 200 years.

41:52.711 --> 41:56.713
Blacks and whites
wiping each other out.

41:58.083 --> 42:01.184
This is our
message to the world.

42:02.487 --> 42:05.388
We're igniting the apocalypse,

42:06.124 --> 42:09.726
and we're the only
ones who'll survive.

42:14.432 --> 42:16.299
Helter Skelter.
